rows.label: tlk41400011_05_msg0001
rows.name: Alst is a complete mess now.

rows.label: tlk41400011_05_msg0002
rows.name:
But strangely, everyone
is conducting their economic
activities as usual.

rows.label: tlk41400011_05_msg0003
rows.name:
There's no looting, and the value
of money hasn't changed...

rows.label: tlk41400011_05_msg0004
rows.name:
Maybe the people of Alst
are surprisingly hopeful.

rows.label: tlk41400011_05_msg0005
rows.name:
So, you should continue to buy and
sell as you always have, and contribute
to the city's economic activity.
